The evidence with the title 'Senate gop plans to repeal obamacare mandate in tax bill ... ' says Nov 14, 2017  ... Sen. John Thune , a member of party leadership, said he is confident a bill that includes the repeal could pass on the Senate floor . He said the revenue saved by eliminating the mandate would allow for further adjustment of tax rates , thereby increasing the measure 's benefits for middle-class earners. 
